{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "交织的火焰 第8章 EX2-1 在遥远的王都……",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "身在狄涅尔帝国帝都的阿尔贝里亚白燕骑士\\n利弗迟迟不愿对帝国倒戈一击。\\n副官帕蒂亚为此焦急不已，却得知利弗\\n是为了收集情报并伺机而动。就在此时，\\n一封神秘的邀请函突然寄到，究竟是谁……"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "第一王子莱昂尼多。\\n还以为王族里也会有友军，结果……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "除尤蒂尔殿下以外\\n就没有能信任的人了吗？\\n难道周围都已经倒向帝国……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "也许吧。\\n不过现在绝望还太早。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "即使所有人都站在帝国那边，\\n也不代表所有人都是敌人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "即使站在帝国那边也不是敌人？\\n这是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我是说，\\n也许会有身在帝国\\n却心系阿尔贝里亚王国的人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "国就像家一样，\\n即使分裂，\\n也会有人心系故所……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n狄涅尔帝国 帝都\\n(旧)王都索尔·阿尔贝里亚\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "一切为了狄涅尔！\\n一切为了狄涅尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_2001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "这次任务辛苦您了，\\n帕蒂亚大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "嗯，辛苦了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "多亏有您，\\n才成功击退了罗卡叛军。\\n如今我军形势占优。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "知道了，你们继续坚守岗位。\\n我回团长那边一趟。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "团长！我已经忍到极限了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "怎么了，帕蒂亚？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你看起来正在气头上啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "你要听从帝国的摆布\\n到什么时候？\\n我们可是白燕骑士团啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "是阿尔贝里亚王室授予了\\n独立权限的崇高骑士团！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "一、白燕骑士团不受任何制约！\\n即使违反国家命令亦然！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "那我们为什么\\n要听从那些家伙的命令？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "只是顺势而为。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "什么顺势而为啊！\\n我不懂！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "团长，我有一个提案。\\n事到如今，唯有与塞西娅大人一战！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "面对丧失心智的塞西娅大人，\\n唯有以死明志！团长，请作出决断！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我明白了……\\n那我就作出决断。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我们要离开王都。\\n差不多该去寻找机会了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "诶诶诶诶，离开王都……\\n我们不去战斗吗？\\n为什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "因为不忍背叛塞西娅大人！？\\n还是说你怕了！？团长！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "都不对，帕蒂亚。\\n白燕骑士团要远征，然后归来。\\n也就是说……\\n",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我们之所以离开王都，\\n是为了将龙带回来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "你说龙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "帝国的人似乎误以为压制住王都，\\n便等于打倒了阿尔贝里亚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "然而阿尔贝里亚的核心，\\n并不是王都。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "并不是王都……\\n那到底是哪里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "阿尔贝里亚的核心，是龙之血。\\n即使所有城市覆灭，只要龙之血尚在，\\n阿尔贝里亚就不会灭亡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "对于举起反旗之人，\\n下一任王定会前来征讨，绝不会错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "为了助其征讨，\\n我们需要留在这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "那迄今为止……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是的，我一直在收集情报。\\n关于帝国到底是什么样的组织。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "不过，已经足够了……\\n养精蓄锐，是时候大展拳脚了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "不愧是团长！\\n居然考虑得如此长远！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "不过，我稍感不服。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "不服什么？因为不能即刻开战吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "不，因为你一直都瞒着我！\\n为什么不告诉我啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "就算告诉你……让你按兵不动收集情报，\\n你也按捺不住吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "肯定会急火攻心，\\n飞奔着离开王都。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "呜呜……\\n这怎么说得准。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我很清楚，因为你是我的部下嘛。\\n好了，既然已经决定了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（该前往何处呢？为了反帝国势力\\n团结一致，首先要去……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（尤蒂尔殿下那里吗？\\n不，还是说……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "白燕骑士",
            "context": "团长！团长！ 有事禀报！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "什么事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "白燕骑士",
            "context": "有一封寄给团长的信。\\n似乎是邀请函……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这种战乱之时还有邀请函？\\n难道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_06_1053",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}